<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Kulmbach</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Klas Pornschlegel den in Nürnberg gefangen Fritz Metzner nicht ausgeliefert hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_129" id="63v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_129_r2l14">Der Stat cʒu Kulmach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_129_r2l15"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> . Vns hat fürgelegt Clas Pornſlegel 
<del rend="strikethrough"> der <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l16">bey vns wonhaft 
<del rend="strikethrough">iſt </del> / vvie daʒ Er bey 
<del rend="strikethrough"> euch </del> vnd v̈mb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l17">euch beſchuldigt ſeẏ woꝛden . daʒ Er den Fricʒen <expan>Mecʒn<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l18">der in vnſer venknüſſe kumen iſt / gen vns . <expan>dargeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l19">vnd verſagt ſüll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> etc </del> / Tu vvir ewr vveiſheit ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l22">vviſſen . daʒ Er des 
<add><ab facs="#facs_129_line_1577033476220_1898">ʒemal </ab></add> vnſchuldig 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſe </del> iſt / vnd wiſʒen 
<del rend="strikethrough">kein </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l23"> <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache 
<del rend="strikethrough">ʒemal </del> von Jm niht / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiij̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r2l24"><expan>Corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> xpi . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_129" id="63v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Kulmach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Clas Pornslegel bey uns
                        wonhaft, wie daz er bey und ümb euch beschuldigt sey worden, daz er den
                        Friczen <expan>Meczn<ex>er</ex></expan>, der in unser venknüsse kumen ist,
                        gen uns <expan>dargeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und versagt süll
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; tu wir ewr weisheit zu wissen, daz er
                        des <add>zemal</add> unschuldig ist und wiszen
                            <expan>sölch<ex>er</ex></expan> sache von im niht.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
